1. *Veze* su se prekinule posle jedne godine. (The ties were broken after one year.)

2. Ona će pokušati da obnovi *vezu*. (She will try to reestablish the relationship.)

3. *Veze* između njih dvoje su se pogoršale. (The connections between the two of them have deteriorated.)

4. Ona se brine o svojim *vezama*. (She worries about her relationships.)

5. Njih dvoje su imali čvrste *veze*. (The two of them had strong ties.)

6. Ona je razvila *vezu* sa njim. (She developed a relationship with him.)